# Data & outputs (regenerated by engine)
/data/*
# Carried corrections only (the LH rebuild's data inputs). data/ohlcv.pkl + data/features.pkl +
# data/_screener_cache/ stay ignored (regenerable; the 64 MB OHLCV is too big for git — pin via a
# release asset, see docs/DATA_AND_ARTIFACTS.md).
